localized_description.zh_CN: Endaxis 是一个专为《明日方舟：终末地》设计的可视化排轴工具。可以通过拖拽技能、建立连线关系来规划战术流程。
localized_description.en_US: Endaxis is a visual skill rotation planner designed for Arknights: Endfield. You can plan tactical processes by dragging skills and establishing connections.

localized_slogan.zh_CN: Endaxis - 《明日方舟：终末地》排轴工具
localized_slogan.en_US: Endaxis - Visual Skill Rotation Planner for Arknights: Endfield

localized_description.zh_CN: 明日方舟：终末地地图集。查看所有地区与副本内的物品与收集品点位详情，并参与构建更完善的游戏内收集体验。
localized_description.en_US: Arknights: Endfield map collection. View details of item and collectible locations in all regions and stages, and contribute to building a more complete in-game collection experience.

localized_slogan.zh_CN: 帮你找到任何你需要的物品与路线。
localized_slogan.en_US: Helping you find any items and routes you need.

localized_description.zh_CN: 高精度自动化助手，专为「明日方舟：终末地」重度作战和最大化效率而设计。
localized_description.en_US: High-precision automation assistant. Designed for heavy-duty operations and maximum efficiency in Arknights: Endfield.

localized_slogan.zh_CN:
MAA - 终
终末地小助手

localized_description.zh_CN: 终末地物品价值、商店与礼包性价比、攒抽计算器，以及更多实用工具。
localized_description.en_US: Item values, shop and package cost performance, gacha calculator, and more practical tools for Endfield.

localized_slogan.zh_CN: 终末地收益相关的数据都在这里
localized_slogan.en_US: All data related to Endfield rewards and returns are here

localized_description.zh_CN: 专为《明日方舟：终末地》打造的工业规划利器。输入目标，生成从资源到成品的最高效率全链条生产方案，让基地扩建精准高效。
localized_description.en_US: A powerful AIC planning tool for Arknights: Endfield. Input your goals to generate the most efficient full-chain production plans from resources to finished products, making base expansion precise and efficient.

localized_slogan.zh_CN: 数据统筹源“石”，效率抢占先机
localized_slogan.en_US: Data-driven resource management, efficiency gains ahead
